  "story_sequence": [
    "1. Arrive from Route 31 (east).",
    "2. Explore Earl's Pokemon Academy (optional, educational content).",
    "3. Challenge Sprout Tower north of city (optional but recommended — Sage Li awards HM05 Flash).",
    "4. Challenge Violet Gym: defeat Bird Keepers Rod and Abe, then Falkner.",
    "5. Receive Zephyr Badge + TM31 Mud-Slap.",
    "6. Elm calls via Pokegear after victory.",
    "7. Visit Pokemon Center — Elm's aide gives Mystery Egg.",
    "8. Continue south on Route 32."
  ],
  "notes": "Violet City is the first gym city. The only mandatory progression gate here is the gym itself. Sprout Tower is optional but gives HM05 Flash needed for Dark Cave. The in-game trade (Kyle: Bellsprout for Onix 'Rocky') is available from first visit. Item balls behind water require Surf (post-Fog Badge). Warp coordinate system uses pokecrystal tile coords (origin top-left). East connection offset=9 from attributes.asm. Sprout Tower entrance warp at x=23,y=5 leads to SPROUT_TOWER_1F."
}
